    "description": "Ishin Co., Ltd. provides media-related business services for local governments and ventures in Japan. The company operates through Public-private Co-creation Project; Global Innovation Business; and Media PR Business segments. It offers various solutions, including Municipal Communication, a media outlet that improves the management capabilities of local governments; and BtoG Platform, which provides support for marketing for local governments online. The company also provides TECHBLITZ, media outlet that connects Japan with the global startup ecosystem and provides information on global startups and ecosystem trends; hosts global innovation training sessions and events specializing in open innovation; invites professors from overseas universities; and operates BLITZ portal, an information portal site. In addition, it offers support for the branding and recruitment of venture companies through media, such as Venture Tsushin, large-scale conferences that mainly bring together growing companies, and the cloud service HIKOMA CLOUD, which produces and operates companies' own recruitment media. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
